---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Pen N" description="About Pen N">
  <section class="grid" style="gap:1.4rem;max-width:72ch;">
    <p class="eyebrow fade-up">About</p>
    <h1 class="fade-up">A practical collaborator with strong frontend instincts.</h1>
    <p class="fade-up">
      I enjoy partnering with teams that care about user outcomes and engineering craft. Most of my recent
      projects involve turning rough product requirements into polished, performant interfaces.
    </p>
    <p class="fade-up">
      My workflow blends design critique, rapid prototyping, and clear handoff. I prioritize clarity in both code
      and communication.
    </p>
    <div class="card fade-up">
      <h2>Working principles</h2>
      <p>Build for maintainability first, then optimize where it matters.</p>
      <p>Keep interfaces calm and legible under real constraints.</p>
      <p>Prefer incremental delivery over big-bang rewrites.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
